insert_aggregate_rating_initial_load.prefix: WITH ins (course_code, year, semester, prof, rmp_difficulty, rmp_helpfulness) AS ( VALUES
insert_aggregate_rating_initial_load.postfix: ) INSERT INTO RATINGAGGR (COURSE_ID, CLASS_ID, RATE_RMP_DIFFICULTY, RATE_RMP_HELPFULNESS) SELECT UNICLASS.COURSE_ID, CLASS.ID, rmp_difficulty, rmp_helpfulness FROM UNICLASS join (SELECT id as COURSE_ID, year, semester, rmp_difficulty, rmp_helpfulness FROM COURSE join ins ON ins.course_code = COURSE.CODE) as temp ON CLASS.COURSE_ID = temp.COURSE_ID AND UNICLASS.YEAR = temp.year AND UNICLASS.SEMESTER = temp.semester;
